WEBVTT

00:00.697 --> 00:04.053
ï»¿2014 was the hottest year on record.

00:04.458 --> 00:06.937
The finding was announced today in a new report...

00:07.116 --> 00:10.292
...from NASA's Goddard Institute for Space Studies in New York.

00:10.929 --> 00:13.675
Since temperature records began in 1880,...

00:14.051 --> 00:17.631
...the global average has increased by 1.4 degrees Fahrenheit.

00:18.153 --> 00:21.722
Scientists expect global and regional fluctuations in temperature...

00:22.001 --> 00:24.689
...from year to year due to changing weather patterns.

00:25.001 --> 00:30.065
When looking at decades worth of data, the ranking of 2014 as the hottest year...

00:30.484 --> 00:34.225
...reinforces the long-term trend of rising global temperatures.

00:34.507 --> 00:38.817
A trend driven by the increase of carbon dioxide levels in the atmosphere.

